6. Networking Cost Comparison

Networking charges were also considered during the comparison.

- AWS charges approximately $0.01 per GB in each direction for inter-Availability Zone (AZ) data transfers.
- Azure charges approximately $0.01 per GB for inter-zone data transfer between Availability Zones.

For this small web application, deployment within a single Availability Zone minimizes networking costs because no significant inter-zone traffic is expected.

