7. Discount Mechanisms

AWS Savings Plans

AWS provides Savings Plans that allow customers to reduce compute costs by committing to one-year or three-year usage. These plans offer lower pricing for long-running workloads compared to standard On-Demand pricing.

Azure Reserved Instances and Azure Hybrid Benefit

Microsoft Azure offers Reserved Virtual Machine Instances and Azure Hybrid Benefit. Reserved Instances reduce virtual machine costs for predictable workloads, while Azure Hybrid Benefit allows organizations with eligible Microsoft licenses to lower Windows virtual machine licensing costs.

